<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
<title>Incoming Referral from The Dot</title>
</head>

<body itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/EmailMessage">

<table class="body-wrap">
	<tr>
		<td></td>
		<td class="container" width="600">
			<div class="content">
				<table class="main" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
					<tr>
						<td class="content-wrap">
							<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
								<tr>
									<td class="content-block">
										<table><tr><td class="middle"><div class="thedotlogo"></div></td><td class="middle"><span class="headertext">The.Dot's Available Photographers</span></td></tr></table>
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td class="content-block">
										Hello {referral.client.fname} {referral.client.lname},
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td class="content-block">
										A little bird ({referringPhotog.fname} {referringPhotog.lname}) told us that you are in the market for a wicked wedding photographer for your big day. We have gone ahead and reached out to all of our members.<br><br>

										The following talented folks are available on your wedding date:
									</td>
								</tr>
								{#availPhotogs}
								<tr>
									<td class="content-block avail-photogs">
											<a href="{profileUrl}">{fname} {lname}</a>
									</td>
								</tr>
								{/availPhotogs}
								<tr>
									<td class="content-block">
										We hope this helps narrowing down your options, and saves you some valuable time looking for a wedding photographer. You can contact each one of these wonderful professionals directly by clicking their name! Check out our blog at <a href="http://www.thedot.photo/blog">http://www.thedot.photo/blog</a> for useful information and tips for your wedding day!</a>
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td class="content-block">
										Thanks again for chosing The.Dot!
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td class="content-block">
										Best regards,<br>
										The.Dot team<br>
										<a href="http://www.thedot.photo">www.thedot.photo</a>
									</td>
								</tr>
							</table>
						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
				<div class="footer">
					<table width="100%">
						<tr>
							<td class="aligncenter content-block">Brought to you by <a href="http://www.thedot.photo">The Dot</a>.</td>
						</tr>
					</table>
				</div></div>
		</td>
		<td></td>
	</tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
